latestIgtvVideos.title: GRW clumsy pri #notamakeuptutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
⚠️Use earphones please🎧 
Hi! 👉🏻👈🏻
So this is basically an introduction of my crackheadness to the world and I'm gonna start with the same old boring speech that I wanted to this since a very very long time and I'm finally doing it! I'm a goofy weird kid and that's exactly what you'll be seeing my videos. This is my first attempt and I'm new to editing and filming so go easy on me! 
I hope you like it cause it's really not as easy as it looks. 
Thanks for watching and let me know your honest opinions! I'm open to positive criticism and I'm sure I need it lol. 
Pls share it if it makes you smile even a lil bit cause we all need to smile a lil more often in such testing, annoying times. 
K peace✌🏻
